# Minimal molecular FF smoke test: single heteronuclear diatomic, NVT.
# Exercises: load_molecular_ff, load_topology, BondedForceProvider,
#            and a real 1-2 pair override distinct from Lorentz-Berthelot mixing.

force_field  molecular

lj_cutoff  8.0

type 1  N  mass 14.007  epsilon 0.0715  sigma 3.310  charge 0.0
type 2  O  mass 15.999  epsilon 0.1200  sigma 3.000  charge 0.0

# Cross-pair override chosen to differ clearly from the configured mixing rule.
pair 1 2  epsilon 0.0100  sigma 1.000

bond_type 1  k 228.0  r0 1.098
